name: Corporate Sponsorship
description:
Corporate sponsorship makes good business sense! In the relentlessly competitive world of business, a strategic alliance with charities and humanitarian organisations is vital.

	Why? Cause programs strengthen vital elements of every successful business through public perception, brand image, and social responsibility.

	So instead of passing the buck, we are stoked in donating 20% of all sales. The current organisation of choice is ‘Surfaid International’ and we need your help! Party hard and stay safe…

	If you have a particular organisations you would like us to donate to, feel free to drop us a line as we are willing to share the love and rotate our support.

name: Cowskin Condom Tin + 3 Condoms
description: Designer Condom Tin + 3 Condoms… The limited edition designer condom tin (love glove) was designed to promote safe sex, and provide a fresh and innovative way to approach promotional merchandise. If you’re looking to get these branded with your company logo, we have negotiated with the manufacturer for a minimum of only a 1000 pieces. Cost is obviously less than the RRP as displayed here, why don’t you get a sample today and contact Ozlat to discuss your requirements. Universal Studios used these tins to promote the launch of ‘40 Year Old Virgin’ and Pink Leopard, a major fashion player is using them as a gift with purchase on their online store. Who’s next?

name: "It's On Like Donkey Kong" Tee
description:
If you got a problem with me then “It’s on like Donkey Kong!” Designed by www.jm-ink.com, this
shirt takes me back to the day when that same club opened up and ran for one night at Bondi. It was a great night, unfortunately it didn’t pack out as it should have and never ran again.

	Look cool without breaking the bank. Our durable, high-quality, pre-shrunk 100% cotton t-shirt is what to wear when you want to go comfortably casual. Preshrunk, durable and guaranteed.

name: Electro Evolution - Men
description:
Electronic music and art have been major influences on the development of the eclectic fashion styles witnessed in today’s society.
